<br>
I would like to know if there is any 'guide' or any material on improving your criticals. I have used the 'search' option, but seems to be broken, does not return result when searching for 'crit' or 'critical' in 'entire message'.<br>
<br>
While I have read that the chance of a crit is purely random,  is there anything that can be done to improve the damage on a crit? I suppose the skill level of Evocation would be important.<br>
<br>
Thanks for any replies. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=azzitay>Azzitay</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 162<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/28/03 5:16 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about criticals</span><hr size=1> Hi,<br>
You have an innate 2% (?) chance to crit , and it goes up i think ... im not sure when u are at low health.<br>
<br>
Im nut sure about that low health , so  dont flame me please.<br>
<br>
At Level 55 you can buy additional AAs to improve Chances on critting ... but thats a looong way. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Baron Azzitay Flammenpfad, Erzverräter des Hauses Tier´Dyrr,<br>
Ratsmitglied <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.der-schatten.com" target="top">Der Schatten</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->,</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Mitglied der freien Raidcommunity <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub59.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.quickJumpTo?id=scarab5467" target="top">SCARAB</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->,</div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center">Organisator der <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub59.ezboard.com/fdiehallenderschattenfrm22" target="top">Deutschen Raidgemeinschaft</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hibashira>Hibashira</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 359<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/28/03 11:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about criticals</span><hr size=1> Innate crit is 2% chance, random, kicks in after level 12, does not increase at all.<br>
<br>
More crit comes from AA abilities:<br>
Spell Casting Fury<br>
Spell Casting Fury Mastery<br>
Fury of Magic Mastery<br>
<br>
There are two things to look at 1) the chance of crit-ing, and 2) the increased damage while crit-ing.  Don't get them confused.<br>
<br>
In any case, if you are not at the AA levels, forget about raising your crits. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=328193"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.geocities.com/hibashirasakai/HibashiraNewHalfSize.txt"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=lemni>Lemni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/28/03 9:46 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Question about criticals</span><hr size=1> Does Dex effect the chance of getting a crit? <p>- Lem<br>
